                    <h3 class='medicalsection__caption'>

                        <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/immunization/overview-of-immunization">
                            免疫接种
                        </a>
                                <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__info'>
                                    <div class='medicalsection__info--text'>免疫力可以通过</div>
                                </i>

                    </h3>

                    <div class='medicalsection__column'>
