                    <h3 class='medicalsection__caption'>

                        <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/approach-to-parasitic-infections/approach-to-parasitic-infections">
                            寄生虫感染
                        </a>
                                <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__info'>
                                    <div class='medicalsection__info--text'>（另请参阅 绦虫, 肠道外原虫, 肠道原虫, 线虫, 和 吸虫等章节.)</div>
                                </i>

                    </h3>

                    <div class='medicalsection__column'>
                        <ul>
                                <li class='medicalsection__link'>
                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__plus--small'></i>
                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__minus--small'></i>
                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/approach-to-parasitic-infections/approach-to-parasitic-infections">寄生虫感染</a>
                                        <ul>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/approach-to-parasitic-infections/approach-to-parasitic-infections#v1012885_zh">原虫</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/approach-to-parasitic-infections/approach-to-parasitic-infections#v1012891_zh">蠕虫</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/approach-to-parasitic-infections/approach-to-parasitic-infections#v29592835_zh">微孢子虫</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__plus--small'></i>
                                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__minus--small'></i>
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/approach-to-parasitic-infections/approach-to-parasitic-infections#v1012915_zh">诊断</a>
                                                        <ul>
