                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/arboviruses-arenaviridae-and-filoviridae/other-arbovirus-infections#v1021141_zh">加利福尼亚脑炎</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/arboviruses-arenaviridae-and-filoviridae/other-arbovirus-infections#v1021146_zh">鄂木斯克出血热和夸赛纳森林病</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/arboviruses-arenaviridae-and-filoviridae/other-arbovirus-infections#v1021151_zh">裂谷热</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/arboviruses-arenaviridae-and-filoviridae/other-arbovirus-infections#v34381241_zh">虫媒病毒参考文献</a>
                                                </li>
                                        </ul>
                                </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class='medicalsection__section'>
                    <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__minus'></i>
                    <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__plus'></i>

                    <h3 class='medicalsection__caption'>

                        <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/bacteria-and-antibacterial-drugs/overview-of-bacteria">
                            细菌和抗细菌药物
                        </a>
                                <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__info'>
                                    <div class='medicalsection__info--text'>细菌是具有环状双链DNA和（除支原体以外）细胞壁的微生物。大多数细菌在细胞外生存。一些细菌（如， <i>Salmonella typhi</i>; <i>Neisseria gonorrhoeae</i>; <i>Legionella</i>, <i>Mycobacterium</i>, <i>Rickettsia</i>, <i>Chlamydia</i>, 和 <i>Chlamydophila</i> 等）倾向于在细胞内生存和复制。一些细菌，如衣原体、<i>Chlamydophila</i>属和立克次体是专性胞内病原菌（即只有在宿主的细胞内方能生长、复制和致病）。其他（如，<i>Salmonella typhi</i>, <i>Brucella</i>sp, <i>Francisella tularensis</i>, <i>N. gonorrhoeae</i>, <i>N. meningitidis</i>, <i>Legionella</i> and <i>Listeria</i> spp, <i>Mycobacterium tuberculosis</i>）是兼性胞内病原菌。</div>
                                </i>

                    </h3>

                    <div class='medicalsection__column'>
                        <ul>
                                <li class='medicalsection__link'>
                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__plus--small'></i>
                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__minus--small'></i>
