                    <h3 class='medicalsection__caption'>

                        <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/nematodes-roundworms/angiostrongyliasis">
                            线虫 （蛔虫）
                        </a>
                                <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__info'>
                                    <div class='medicalsection__info--text'>管圆线虫病是一种由管圆线虫<i>Angiostrongylus</i>属的蚴虫感染所导致的疾病；根据感染的虫种的不同可出现肠道症状或嗜酸性粒细胞脑膜炎。</div>
                                </i>

                    </h3>

                    <div class='medicalsection__column'>
                        <ul>
                                <li class='medicalsection__link'>
                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__plus--small'></i>
                                        <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__minus--small'></i>
                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/nematodes-roundworms/angiostrongyliasis">管圆线虫病</a>
                                        <ul>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/nematodes-roundworms/angiostrongyliasis#v8986856_zh">诊断</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/nematodes-roundworms/angiostrongyliasis#v8986859_zh">治疗</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/nematodes-roundworms/angiostrongyliasis#v29656209_zh">预防</a>
                                                </li>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/nematodes-roundworms/angiostrongyliasis#v29656215_zh">关键点</a>
                                                </li>
                                        </ul>
