                    <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__minus'></i>
                    <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__plus'></i>

                    <h3 class='medicalsection__caption'>

                        <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/sexually-transmitted-diseases-stds/overview-of-sexually-transmitted-diseases">
                            （STDs） 性传播疾病
                        </a>
                                <i class='medicalsection__icon medicalsection__info'>
                                    <div class='medicalsection__info--text'>性传播疾病（sexually transmitted diseases，STDs）又称为性传播感染（sexually transmitted infections，STIs），其致病微生物在大小、生命周期、感染部位、对现有药物敏感性等方面差异很大。</div>
                                </i>

                    </h3>

