                                        <ul>
                                                <li class="medicalsection__link--single medicalsection__link__inside">
                                                    <a href="/professional/infectious-diseases/spirochetes/bejel-pinta-and-yaws#v1007929_zh">症状和体征</a>
                                                </li>
